Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.13,0:01:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.55,0:01:21.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.83,0:01:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊织她们还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微有点堵车
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.08,0:01:30.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还以为我是最后一个呢
