Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.01,0:01:33.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.83,0:01:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊织她们说有工作所以来不了了…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:39.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.26,0:01:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要全员集合有点困难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.98,0:01:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.00,0:01:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这才新年演唱会全员练习的第一天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:53.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法  我们自己先练习一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.60,0:01:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.78,0:01:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离演唱会也没多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:01:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.06,0:02:01.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…其实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.11,0:02:02.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.82,0:02:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了
