Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  大家都很可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是我的自信之作
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.21,0:06:22.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟是新年第一场演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.23,0:06:23.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然现在大家真的很忙碌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日程表也那个样子  很辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:31.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是大家齐心协力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.35,0:06:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会是一场非常棒的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  大家一起加油吧  制作人先生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.43,0:06:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  大家团结哦  团结
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合大家的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.14,0:06:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让这次演唱会成功哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:55.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此大家必须配合好时间一起练习哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.44,0:06:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然离正式演出没多少时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.01,0:07:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.92,0:07:10.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  天海小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:14.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以谈一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会占用多少时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.67,0:07:23.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  唯独今天实在不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.90,0:07:25.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.31,0:07:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.45,0:07:41.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.06,0:07:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.55,0:07:50.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水濑小姐和我那霸小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.45,0:07:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为上一份工作实在无法抽身了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:56.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.88,0:08:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚美她们也是  拍摄还没结束的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我替她们向春香说声抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.15,0:08:07.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}春香  非常抱歉的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}飞机误点了  现在在羽田的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:18.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希看来也不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然要全员一起练习很难呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.42,0:08:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明去年全员一起练习了很久的说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.26,0:08:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就以这里的成员多多练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.04,0:08:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把今天的录像拿给那些不能来的人看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我去借摄像机
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.20,0:08:51.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  真
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梓小姐  麻烦帮我压一下腰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.00,0:08:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  要好好热一下身呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.88,0:08:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.94,0:08:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一  二
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.48,0:09:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1  2  3  4
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.46,0:09:14.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天起得很早吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.73,0:09:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…咦  为什么千早会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.35,0:09:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听音无小姐说了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,定期广播的录音  提前到早上了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.45,0:09:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然今天的练习就来不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.47,0:09:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作人员说如果是这样的话  就答应了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.10,0:09:40.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千早？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.01,0:09:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去拜托制作人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:51.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮我把明天开始的国外录音延后一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.71,0:09:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也不能认同这种状态下的演唱会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:09:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行呀  千早
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.71,0:10:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须得去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.08,0:10:02.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春香…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.62,0:10:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作人先生说了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.16,0:10:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次的国外录音将会影响到千早今后的发展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.38,0:10:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以也做足了准备
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.92,0:10:23.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家心里也都想练习的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不过新年演唱会那天必须回来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.01,0:10:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.19,0:10:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.26,0:10:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.24,0:10:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然会有点寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.64,0:10:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.49,0:10:58.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个提议
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.21,0:11:01.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下一次全员练习之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.80,0:11:06.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起工作的同事也开始小人数的练习如何
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.18,0:11:10.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一定一定会更好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家一起加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.47,0:11:17.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才是搞什么嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.98,0:11:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.05,0:11:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边穷酸的两位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.10,0:11:24.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.91,0:11:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来没这么快结束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.61,0:11:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个人开始先练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.11,0:11:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  春春  已经没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.07,0:11:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那明天的全员练习一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.01,0:11:55.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  我是天海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.48,0:12:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  今天的全员练习只能中止了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.72,0:12:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实在搞不定大家的行程
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  欢迎回来  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.86,0:12:15.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  制作人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哦  虽然是在电话谈事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.14,0:12:31.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.56,0:12:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不  那个不管怎样都要把客人和偶像的热情放在第一位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是属于每一个人的765事务的演唱会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.79,0:12:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.63,0:13:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  昨天真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:12.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在去工作室的路上又被叫回去了  所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.67,0:13:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说了没关系了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.38,0:13:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个昨天在电话里听你说了好多遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个  离正式开场还有时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和雪步三人一起来做演唱会的练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:30.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  还是先以今天的直播为重点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.57,0:13:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little  Match  Girl是首次披露的新歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.44,0:13:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且还是现场直播  不可以失败
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.25,0:13:48.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪步也在努力承受着主唱的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.48,0:13:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也好好努力吧  在这个瞬间上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.39,0:14:33.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春香  我这次没有失败哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好厉害啊  雪步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雪步  太帅了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.19,0:14:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  真
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.18,0:14:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  这周也到结束的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.07,0:14:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下周再见
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:51.27,temp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}好  直播吗Sunday！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:51.27,temp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}本周也到结束的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:51.27,temp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}下周再见  1  2！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  1  2
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.88,0:14:55.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直播吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.65,0:14:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sunday！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.80,0:15:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  OK
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.47,0:15:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天有点过火啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.07,0:15:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身子好痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.26,0:15:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希  不快点的话就赶不上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.98,0:15:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天好像也不能去练习了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.81,0:15:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好看台词啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.72,0:15:29.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都留下来稍微等会  有事要说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.02,0:15:36.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腰斩？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.45,0:15:37.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.06,0:15:39.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.25,0:15:40.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是收视率的问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  收视率很好的哦  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也想继续的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是其它节目投诉  叫我们不要把整个周日都霸占下来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.06,0:15:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是受过照顾的节目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.27,0:16:01.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想办法通融过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.38,0:16:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.32,0:16:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个很有趣的节目的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.16,0:16:11.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有始必有终
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.77,0:16:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  总之好好加油到最后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯嗯  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.52,0:16:21.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  要欢乐有趣到最终回啊  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.02,0:16:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.19,0:16:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊织  路上一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:30.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吗  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.02,0:16:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给  音乐剧的行程表
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.61,0:16:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排演是明天的20点开始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.26,0:16:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那个时间是大家一起练习的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个工作对春香和美希来说会是非常重要的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:16:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是「和演唱会比哪个重要」的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.71,0:17:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不论多么的冷  我还会继续梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.76,0:17:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的梦想多如繁星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:13.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所追求的是  像那太阳一样光辉灿烂  熊熊燃烧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.20,0:17:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天海  换你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:17.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:23.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听好了  我可是打算从你们两个中选主角出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:26.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之拿出你们的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.29,0:17:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,展现你们的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这个角色上展现自己的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.57,0:17:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息时间是10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.73,0:17:53.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和传闻一样是个很严格的舞台导演呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.94,0:17:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  但是美希觉得没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.56,0:18:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和美希一起真好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是我一个人的话大概就消沉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不知道谁会成为主角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.65,0:18:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:15.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.41,0:18:18.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希绝对要演主角
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.92,0:18:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这是honey给我的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让honey看成为主角的我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想和「一起加油」是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.66,0:19:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,制作人？  今天还没看见他呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是跟着谁去工作现场了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:26.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么急事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.45,0:19:29.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我在的时候回来的话  要让他打电话给你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.34,0:19:35.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦了  我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要歌唱  为了那高贵的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.18,0:19:53.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.71,0:20:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息时间是15分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.11,0:20:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  没什么精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来现场慰问了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:33.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舞台如何  开心吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.09,0:20:37.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.61,0:20:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且能学习的地方很多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.31,0:20:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:51.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你昨天来事务所了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:57.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是有什么事要和我说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,honey  你来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美希
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.51,0:21:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个啊  美希很努力的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.07,0:21:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师的训话结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:29.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  才不是训话  是演出指导
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:30.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  对不起对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.40,0:21:32.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  美希
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到铜锣烧了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  有铜锣烧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.94,0:21:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  已经交给工作人员了  快去吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  honey的铜锣烧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.51,0:21:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不是蜂蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:48.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.10,0:21:51.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:55.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.34,0:22:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.41,0:22:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事…  你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.97,0:22:10.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  真的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.56,0:22:26.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人掉下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.42,0:22:30.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快叫救护车
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:32.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么升降台没升上来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.58,0:23:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我…  错了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.00,0:24:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我那么任性
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.59,0:24:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才会变成这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.82,0:24:08.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二十四话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.98,0:24:09.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,--------------IN--------------
