Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:25.72,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}全てを恋で染めたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:30.05,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}どんなデキゴトも超えてゆける強さ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.58,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}キミがボクにくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.07,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}「大人になったらね」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:56.51,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ちょっと油断してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:59.41,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}キミの横顔をね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.38,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}みているのよ  まだ今でも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:07.53,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}ほらね  気付いたら？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:10.82,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}同じ  眼の高さ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:14.65,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}いつの間にか少女じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.69,songjp,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}驚くでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.07,0:00:21.95,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}因为有你的余温  七彩纽扣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:25.72,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}一切都染上恋爱的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:30.05,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}克服一切困难那坚强的心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.58,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}也是你给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:52.07,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}「长大之后呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.04,0:00:56.51,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}有点大意了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.64,0:00:59.41,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}现在也看着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:03.38,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你的侧脸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:07.53,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}你看  发现了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.59,0:01:10.82,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}个子已经一样高了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.91,0:01:14.65,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}不知不觉间稚气已经褪去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.65,0:01:16.69,songcn,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)}吓了一跳吧？
